{"tid":1631106,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 急！求大家修正抗爭嘅路線","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:23.000Z","uid":121001,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"202a7c1ea90f09802282cefd7a175a463aeaa274","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"首先想多謝一位應屆DSE考生既文，我再做左補充。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可 係要對抗政權！冇咗民意我哋只會變成一班爛仔<br />\n大家裝修私了我唔係唔支持，但係燒銀行、燒電訊公司，打只不過係政見唔同嘅人（如果對方先出手當然可以召喚神獸自衛），咁樣落去好多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淺黃會離我地而去</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我阿媽本身係深黃，由六九一路上街到今日都冇停，之前好多次我地做錯咗嘅嘢佢都寧願接受，但係去到今次，佢話佢好驚我哋會變咗林鄭口中嘅「真暴徒」！手足可能會話要黃嘅會繼續黃，錯L曬！冇咗民意，我哋所做嘅就冇咗正當性，當我地冇咗市民嘅支持，我哋就冇辦法堂堂正正咁繼續抗爭！到時候只係我哋小撮人繼續為我哋自己嘅理想抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n美國嗰邊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原本</span></span>人權法案<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好順利</span></span>，但係臨政府、大量裝修難睇嘅畫面令到美國嗰邊開始反對示威者，如果人權法案通過唔到， 咁就大鑊！<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家諗清楚我哋上街係為咗啲咩，我哋係為咗五大訴求缺一不可，要爭取呢D訴求係要向政權對抗！<br />\n我都好嬲啲藍絲，但係你想純粹洩憤跟住失去民意，定係忍住把火，聚焦民意全民對抗政府？<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化<br />\n<br />\n如果勇武抗爭再走落去，每日我地損失既就係被捕義士，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一日一百至二百個</span></span>要面臨被狗打，同埋被控暴動，虐待動物同非法集結，依家加埋蒙面法。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">值得我地失去咁多真香港人咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n日日幫對家裝修唔會幫到我地好多，反而比機會真暴徒，黑警，南亞幫趁機偷野，放火，破壞，之後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地手足被控</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n依家勝利在望既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線</span></span>，而國際戰線需要既係耐性，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n主線國家<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span></span>既香港人權法案係需要時間通過。人地都有自己既問題要解決，好似貿易戰，通烏門。<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英國</span></span>已經有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">58位</span></span>議員話中國違反一國兩制。係人都知英國做野慢，加上佢地仲受脫歐問題困擾緊。<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 加拿大保守黨</span></span>已經宣佈支持香港示威者，承諾當選後會支持香港示威者，通過加拿大版既美國香港人權民主法案。<br />\n<br />\n支線國家<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬來西亞</span></span>總統叫柒婆下台<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡</span></span>金融上不斷吸收香港資金<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">印尼</span></span>記者採訪有一隻眼失明<br />\n<br />\n要記住一樣野，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際上我地贏到七彩</span></span>，需要既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間發酵</span></span>，其他國家都有自己家事要處理，如果日日勇武就會將淺黃轉番做淺藍為求自保。<br />\n<br />\n另外，緊急法下既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">司法覆核</span></span>都係需要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時間</span></span>去上訴，雖然我唔熟law，但高等法院唔係final decision maker。希望有熟law既朋友補充。但上訴，都係需要時間架。最後都係要，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪日日都等，等等下就做到野，我可以話比你聽，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n喺等既過程中，我地需要做既唔單止focus 喺 twitter, reddit 同 Facebook. 我地仲可以做海外文宣，連儂牆等。但終極最有效既方法，一定係全民三罷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span></span>唔係話做到就做到，因為需要既係組織各行各業先做到，請唔同業界既大家勇躍參與。喺三罷期間可以做咩? 我個人覺得地區性活動又好，留係屋企做野又好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之要罷</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n一個和理非香港人上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e522aaf53f298a423a23d3aff3c4b8c569d7e9dc","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n1/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c4709623682a156033c01f3bda932f512b53a4","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae1deaf75158d24a117fe4fd69c1bd505f5bec5","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc069c718942708c87a3378b490ca510842c5484","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"4/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d676a745021962ed290964ef130edd2a47b74b3b","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9b6ef7cfdb9ae342436a77b7e9cbd0592fb20c24","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"6/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da8f7a57dc76aa0370cf4febbb338cf37b9176d","tid":1631106,"uid":258572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:48:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ecd84f6194610e27add3d0cf1cd299f0f10c0cd","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"7/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b3d327f90fb15386426ca6684c5509d46004dd","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:48:57.000Z","msg":"8/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144bbcde2804b25ec5e8d5b85ec3cd11c0b49a75","tid":1631106,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL1JiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=186784b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"af54d202587012e385ada7f370e80c0d97c47d14","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"9/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5647396354969688961c46d52bb16159c37d115","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"10/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4add374ffe4c296547bf4cb5722e922f6debdf7d","tid":1631106,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"無大規模裝修根本唔會出現真正既全民三罷<br />\n完"},{"pid":"50cd2834e6678771a755d14232af11a95cda91c9","tid":1631106,"uid":226779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"幫推 好有用"},{"pid":"2a000839e113a9565c2896faf0181e328fa70c46","tid":1631106,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:55:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb321309103e45da84f389910024d9cf0a0906c8","tid":1631106,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb3915f1b0ccad607cd685a8d64a91c5fe4e2140","tid":1631106,"uid":222305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abe732eb188cfc52615a4cad2b12f3bf683befcf","tid":1631106,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"由古至今<br />\n每一場戰爭，社運，抗爭<br />\n都係增加政治籌碼既手段<br />\n呢個係人類社會既一種特色<br />\n<br />\n好多人唔明白，我地既政治籌碼暫時已經足夠<br />\n現階段係要文宣，打國際線，例如<br />\n整理所有黑警暴行，被捕人士既資訊<br />\n統一之後sd比外國議員<br />\n<br />\n抗爭唔同做運動<br />\n唔係多多益善，少少無拘<br />\n有時候係需要停落黎，等話到事既人去傾<br />\n我地都只係凡人，唔係當權者<br />\n所以係要耐心去忍耐<br />\n<br />\n問題係林鄭宜家強推緊急法<br />\n手足唔上街就會比位佢入<br />\n就算上街都會比佢話更加證明要立法<br />\n立於不敗之地，厚顏無恥<br />\n<br />\n我地宜家需要諗方法拆左佢先<br />\n唔係點做都只會陷入被動<br />\n手足上街既意義會愈黎愈細，再加上裝修同神獸<br />\n好容易會被港共抺黑，令到儲係手既政治籌碼清袋<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話，屌你啦<br />\n家下打仗梗係靠自己，等美國出手我地啲手足都含撚啦<br />\n問題係，我地香港暫時都唔係一個國家<br />\n何況我地仲要冇武裝去真係打仗<br />\n<br />\n要記住我地既做法，係需要外國介入，幫我地拎番自治權<br />\n姐係要睇外國臉色<br />\n美國宜家係唔想我地獨立，想利用我地搵支那錢，但係又唔想支那完全控制我地"},{"pid":"5aa252d0feb5dbc478f2ea35558422fde553210f","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4add374ffe4c296547bf4cb5722e922f6debdf7d","tid":1631106,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"無大規模裝修根本唔會出現真正既全民三罷<br />\n完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"如果你想幫人裝修<br />\n我唔會阻你<br />\n對家係黑幫<br />\n我更加支持你<br />\n我只係想手足少被捕少流血"},{"pid":"b7efd8f63d07eecf357390b79ef6d81a265c4ef0","tid":1631106,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa252d0feb5dbc478f2ea35558422fde553210f","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4add374ffe4c296547bf4cb5722e922f6debdf7d","tid":1631106,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"無大規模裝修根本唔會出現真正既全民三罷<br />\n完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"如果你想幫人裝修<br />\n我唔會阻你<br />\n對家係黑幫<br />\n我更加支持你<br />\n我只係想手足少被捕少流血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"ok一齊加油"},{"pid":"8b2ec5aa6e76869af5a2124ec084878e30d237a5","tid":1631106,"uid":120295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea9b2e052b2dc53f6493c4536544245f189592f","tid":1631106,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無大規模裝修根本唔會出現真正既全民三罷<br />\n完</blockquote>如果你想幫人裝修<br />\n我唔會阻你<br />\n對家係黑幫<br />\n我更加支持你<br />\n我只係想手足少被捕少流血</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重申 <br />\n<br />\n勇武同和理非<br />\n<br />\n不割席<br />\n不被捕<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不流血<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n我既諗法係要大多和理非響應先做到<br />\n裝修過後係被罷工，意義唔同"},{"pid":"59cbef0a9cbff708812aafb36924cb48902d5035","tid":1631106,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"都幾同意，美國果面佢地都留意緊"},{"pid":"83bf7af0de0b2369a36050ba2ed8d2e1d3805a84","tid":1631106,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}